title: Hector's Shed
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little cafe providing breakfast and lunch. Veg choices in panini sandwiches, wraps, and has a 'vegan bowl' with hummus, avocado, olives and fresh bread. Keeps soya milk for hot drinks. There is a veggie breakfast on the menu, which could potentially be veganized but ask.
